    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>tofu</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to a bowl with your <strong>soy</strong> <strong>sauce</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until all the tofu is coated – this is your <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>tofu</strong></p>",
