      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>tofu</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-6 min, turning occasionally until golden and crisp</p><p>Whilst the tofu is cooking, chop the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673871539480-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673871539480-x400.jpg",
