          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673871539480-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is golden, add the <strong>chopped courgette </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Whilst the courgette is cooking, add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>tortiglioni </strong>for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>tortiglioni</strong>, reserving 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[115ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml] </span><strong>starchy</strong> <strong>pasta</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1673871545237-x200.jpg",
