            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, transfer the <strong>courgette</strong> and <strong>tofu</strong> to a plate and set aside, reserve the pan</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and add 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min or until a sandy paste forms – this is your <strong>roux</strong></p><p>Gradually whisk in the <strong>pea & chive sauce </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
